WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:06.000
The vendor says the orchard sensor kit can cut water use by twenty percent.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.000
In the field, the cheap probes drifted after two foggy nights, which the sponsored case study did not mention.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
This might be wrong, but local salinity may explain the yield bump more than the sensor software.
